## About SMOPYC

SMOPYC is the 20th International Fair for Public Works, Construction and Mining Machinery held in Zaragoza, Spain. As one of Southern Europe's largest construction equipment exhibitions, it attracts major manufacturers and buyers from Spain, Portugal, and beyond.

## Exhibition Scope

Construction Machinery | Mining Equipment | Public Works Machinery | Road Construction | Material Handling | Components & Parts

## Event Scale

**600+ Exhibitors** and **50,000+ Visitors** make SMOPYC a major event in the global construction equipment calendar, offering comprehensive product displays and live demonstrations.

## Why Attend

Access the Spanish and Portuguese construction markets, discover European equipment innovations, connect with distributors and contractors, and explore business opportunities in Southern European construction and mining sectors.
